---
title: Garlicky Fried Chicken Sandwiches with Honey Mustard Mayo & Roasted Carrots
description: Think you need a fancy meal to really treat your tastebuds? These fried chicken sandwiches beg to differ! Chicken cutlets are spread with sour cream, coated in garlicky panko, and fried until golden and crispy. Toasted buns are stuffed with chicken and a layer of spicy honey-mustard mayo, and the rest of that tangy-sweet dipper is served on the side with roasted carrot fries. It’s casual, downhome comfort food at its finger lickin’ finest!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlicky-fried-chicken-sandwiches-751058ad.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/garlicky-fried-chicken-sandwiches-628c062e224bec358d0033c0-759a8ce3.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/garlicky-fried-chicken-sandwiches-628c062e224bec358d0033c0
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 930 kcal
